verbose_text: Lastly, transcription of Cd5 and Nr4a1 (encoding Nur77), which could be indicative of the strength of TCR signaling experienced by env specific CD4 + T cells, did not significantly differ between Gzmb - and Gzmb + cells (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY C), suggesting that TCR signal strength is not the primary determinant of CD4 + CTL differentiation.
